Usage:
- Place folder in latex search path
  Command to get this path on Ubuntu (linux): 
  kpsepath tex | tr : '\n' | grep home
- Use package ntb as theme in preamble of beamer document
  \usetheme{ntb}
- Define \autor{}, \institute{}, \title{} and \date{} in preamble
- If you dont want to show the footer on the title page:
  {
  \setbeamertemplate{footline}{}
  \maketitle
  }
